  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781490/extras/30ba88c75f6ff8a0b4693360ab3d0201.webp?t=1687944930\" width=600 height=63 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>In the deep universe, there’s a special planet.  On this planet, lives a mysterious little creature who has two green leaves on its head and the great power to change the gravity around it. One day, a rift appears in the sky, something fallen from the rift with the dazzling light shining like a meteor.<br>Seeing this, the little one decides to start the journey and find out what happened.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781490/extras/2acfbc53727e9cfb01e53c074ab07f6d.webp?t=1687944930\" width=600 height=52 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2>Rotate the worlds to solve puzzles and avoid dangers, lead the little monster to the destination safely.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781490/extras/7a0a1dde2d71ddc9914e31b090e0686e.poster.avif?t=1687944930\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781490/extras/7a0a1dde2d71ddc9914e31b090e0686e.webm?t=1687944930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGING LEVELS</h2>Dark forest, waste lands and freezing plains.  Various kinds of levels and items to make your journey fulfilled with challenge. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781490/extras/9f2f7088fb353d521f80f2b74e866b11.avif?t=1687944930\" width=600 height=533 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781490/extras/d35d2ac6e45f1e92c5c28a7963331ee5.avif?t=1687944930\" width=600 height=88 /></span>",
